  ID: 0
  Name: Shield
  Type: Cast
  Icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 69c45055bf0011842975ce2007fefafa, type: 3}
  Description: When the player activates the assigned ability, they generate a shield
    that reduces incoming damage. The ability is sustained by holding down the input
    and ends when the key is released. While the shield is active, an energy bar
    is displayed and gradually depletes over time. Once the energy bar is fully depleted,
    the shield disappears and cannot be activated again until the bar has completely
    recharged. The energy bar refills passively while the shield is not in use. The
    player cannot use multiple shields simultaneously. To activate a different shield,
    the current one must be released first. Each shield has its own independent energy
    bar. When the shield touches an enemy or their projectiles, an Impact is triggered.
